Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:49.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:06.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:20.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:25.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:32.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:43.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫日暮戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生于一个\N历史很悠久很古老的神社里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个非常平凡的国三女生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就在我十五岁生日那天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社的井里\N突然出现了一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我带回到了战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那里\N遇到了一个半妖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N可以增强妖怪法力的宝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了跟犬夜叉他们\N一起寻找散落各处的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始来往于\N现代与战国之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想借四魂之玉的力量\N满足自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫奈落的妖怪为了从\N犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到完美的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意将杀生丸引进奈落城里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正当奈落打算吞了杀生丸\N将他化成自己的一部分的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉偏偏破了奈落的结界\N跑进奈落城来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在千钧一发之际\N救兵及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为一辈子\N都能逃出我的手掌心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落利用珊瑚的弟弟\N琥珀做他的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁机逃之夭夭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此\N真的从我们的面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第82话 奔波于现代与战国之间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恶了  奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道以后\N他都不再回这座城了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连结界都被你破除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又怎么能搬走这座城堡呢\N你说对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定\N真的可以砍死奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏就差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N总算又可以回到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算回到了这个安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻松松的念书了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想\N还真有点对不起犬夜叉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得大家现在好不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个公式  后天一定会考哦\N大家回去要牢牢的把它背住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都什么时候了\N还在担心别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩两天\N要是不赶快抱抱佛脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候恐怕要补考那就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  可以走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你啦  借我笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们自己也要复习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托拜托一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只借一下下\N就还给你们总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  谁叫你这么弱不禁风\N一天到晚生病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你们一定会帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就拿去影印一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得这么可怜\N我们哪敢不借呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就谢谢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家开动吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在胡思乱想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想什么还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是那个\N爱吃醋的小太保是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你发展到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天才见过他哥哥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说见过他哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他哥哥恐怕也是太保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他哥哥这么凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他哥哥应该更厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们兄弟俩只要一碰面\N经常都会打架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两兄弟都不是好惹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你打算继续这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心你将来吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒认为\N爱可以克服一切障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我借走笔记了  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学生正在考试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的目的都跟戈薇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么办?要去排队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是影印去哪里都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到其他地方去印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么到处都这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞么鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝…祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是些没有义气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这家伙\N不晓得为什么去那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说好了\N马上就会回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对\N她说过要待两三天才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么每一个人\N都好像没事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落从我们手中跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你也应该养足精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才有力气继续对付奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不像你们几个家伙\N这么不堪一击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不觉得疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种打法\N普通人还真是受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己身子差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好意思怪别人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的邪气还阴魂不散呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都让那些死魂虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙寻找他那股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次偏偏\N连结界的位置都感应不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底奈落那股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上从琥珀身上\N取下四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你只当\N这个小子是个傀儡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不会\N帮你解决那个人质姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会送上门让杀生丸杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再这么继续反抗奈落下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看\N你恐怕没多少日子可活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光会说别人  而我自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连琥珀也一起不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来弥勒法师\N特地去安慰珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇早就跟我说过\N珊瑚一定在偷偷期待琥珀回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  我可以坐一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子你还在担心\N你弟弟的事对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说有点强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你真的要放宽心才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我能够了解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候\N你是不是想一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要说的就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  弥勒法师最恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装要安慰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是想趁机吃豆腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天等很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不早点跟我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的声音特别清脆好听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个都只会偷懒\N一点都不知道上进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N还是得自己挑灯夜战了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一点都看不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  请问哲子在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在电话里问问也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚在电话里面问了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  你的课本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果昨天一整天\N什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  姐姐  告诉你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打断我听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易背住了\N又让你给打断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天再背不起来的话\N真的会完蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是专程来接你的  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  马上跟我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要捣乱好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考试了你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发什么小姐脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我乖乖的  知不知道\N绝对不可以到外头去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待在家里你听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  我傍晚就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇忘了把便当带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得能不能麻烦你跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沿着戈薇身上的气味找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很快可以追上她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮忙  马上给我抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚  全都给我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子\N你活得不耐烦了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来戈薇她们这个时代\N也安全不到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发什么呆啊  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥  谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要命\N这世界怎么乱成这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉怎么会在这里出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是你叫坐下的吧\N麻烦你站起来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门前不是跟你说过\N叫你千万不要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人托我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人托你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的便当耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道专程替我送便当来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都挤成一堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家里温书\N根本就没有办法专心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N只好在图书馆待到天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点念就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肋间神经痛好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻居然身体那么差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要好好锻炼才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一些对健康有益的食谱\N是我特别搜集来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿回去试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条这个人真的好细心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚怎么没有想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然忘了跟北条借笔记来看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  突然想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个中药偏方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说对各种病都很有帮助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  戈薇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体健康呢最重要的是情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让自己的生活有规律
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三餐也要定时定量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇同学  记得一定要吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真倒霉  还是没有借到笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刚刚说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一位\N身穿红衣身轻如燕的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后紧要关头\N帮忙抓到了强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位年轻人的\N英勇事迹不只这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还帮消防队\N救出被困在大火中的小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那位年轻人的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是刚刚我戴的帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去学校之前你到底做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别说这些  这盒子装什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书都念不完了  还在吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  你进来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我陪犬夜叉哥哥玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥  我们去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续看书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂都还没有冲掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不玩了\N出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你出去你听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公式又忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头快烧掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是辣到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你自己像饿死鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到东西就往嘴里塞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么叫\N你很烦知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样一直看着我\N我会分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你还是躺下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己笨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你眼睛不看着前面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N明天可以跟我回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子\N难道打算整晚都盯着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么精力充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡  睡着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不晓得这小子搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家要温书偏偏来搅局
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉这副熟睡的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前还真的没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最忙最累的一向就是他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少今天晚上\N你可以好好的睡一觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你昨天晚上\N在戈薇家过夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你昨天晚上\N整晚都霸占我的床
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我连模拟考都考砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可恶的人就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:40.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:47.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:54.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:24:01.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:07.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:14.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:21.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:27.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:34.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:41.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.80,0:24:48.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:54.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.65,0:24:58.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.77,0:25:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始发问
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片  根本不在奈落手里\N你说会是谁拿走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.48,0:25:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我数数\N在琥珀背上有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.71,0:25:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇手里还有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停  时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族的钢牙\N两只脚上也有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一钢牙也被奈落抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.19,0:25:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点你放心  奈落现在不知道\N躲到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.76,0:25:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?这又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.96,0:25:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族少女和月虹的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.93,0:25:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说妖狼族少女
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.46,0:25:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了还有钢牙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
